entries.femaleVariant: Listen, baby… listen. I'd do anything... for you. Let's kick all this in the ass, huh? Fuck off to the Caymans or some--
Uh-huh. An' what would the missus say?
Don't worry your head about that, hotbuns... that's my thing. Get a quickie divorce... an' if she wants to battle it out, there are ways… Get my meaning?
Mhm. Perfectly. An' I don't mean to rush you or nothin', but you just ran out your hour.
No problem, I'll just pay you for another…What'd you say your name was? Candy? Mandy? Oh, what's it fuckin' matter…?
